Lensa is one of the many named citizens of Rellekka and can be found near the entrance. At level 45 Thieving and after The Fremennik Trials, this npc can be pickpocketed for 40 coins and 65 Thieving experience.

A Smelly journal can be found in the ruined fishing hamlet to the east of the Wintertodt Camp. Written inside are the voyages of Larkur, presumably Lensa's lover or admirer as each entry starts with "Dearest Lensa."
